@startuml
title Veterinary Open API Platform - System Architecture

actor Admin
actor Developer
actor "API Consumer\n(Clinic / App)" as Consumer

cloud "Web Interface / API Gateway" as Interface {
  component "Admin Dashboard\n(React)" as AdminUI
  component "Developer Dashboard\n(React)" as DevUI
  component "Public API\n(/animals/*)" as PublicAPI
}

component "Backend Server\n(Node.js + Express)" as Backend
database "Database\n(MySQL)" as DB

' ===== Admin Flow =====
Admin --> AdminUI : Login / CRUD Developer\nManage API Keys
AdminUI --> Backend : REST API (JWT Auth)
Backend --> DB : CRUD Admin, Users, API Keys
DB --> Backend
Backend --> AdminUI : JSON Response

' ===== Developer Flow =====
Developer --> DevUI : Login / Generate API Key\nAPI Docs / Playground
DevUI --> Backend : REST API (JWT Auth)
Backend --> DB : Read Users / API Keys
DB --> Backend
Backend --> DevUI : JSON Response

' ===== Public API Flow =====
Consumer --> PublicAPI : HTTP Request\nx-api-key
PublicAPI --> Backend : Validate API Key\nFetch Vet Data
Backend --> DB : Read Veterinary Data
DB --> Backend
Backend --> PublicAPI : JSON Response
PublicAPI --> Consumer : API Response

@enduml
